{"tid":1681762,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港偽黃港豬特色IG抗爭","createTime":"2019-10-29T15:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T08:25:50.000Z","uid":193485,"like":50,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"44fd0a5f15fb3a879161db5a91dd6434ab638ea2","tid":1681762,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:38:05.000Z","msg":"屌哂你班港豬，個個係IG share個post就當自己做咗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時就排隊食個龍門打個卡就好似好偉大咁<br />\n約親出去發夢都話自己唔得閒冇時間，第日要返工好辛苦乜乜柒柒諸多藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出嚟既人就愈嚟愈少，平時講到幾嬲幾嬲，屌哂班狗老母，一有活動就淨係識做鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾我睇死你班港豬，11月2一定唔夠100萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實多你一個真係好多<br />\n11.2 維園見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZRtNCF4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZRtNCF4.jpg&h=b3a4342f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cf2c61958e8eadc02a524759ddb5038906b5bdb7","tid":1681762,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd0bcec7affa5fedd04b8be0dcdfe8cfff6f3e5","tid":1681762,"uid":198590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:39:38.000Z","msg":"到時見<br />\n我應承你"},{"pid":"5fef79b405403bb2a94b691cc9a48cc4a5f21fa8","tid":1681762,"uid":193485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:40:43.000Z","msg":"大家一齊call馬"},{"pid":"9d75443c65518bec1532aab66b35707075916eb0","tid":1681762,"uid":38904,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"有個asso同學前幾日先屌完蒙面法<br />\n今日見佢返深圳食袋底撈<img src